From John Luther Subject Re Freemasonry and the Southern Baptist Convention In article Tony Alicea writes With the Southern Baptist Convention convening this June to consider the charges that Freemasonry is incompatible with christianity I thought the following quotes by James Holly the Anti Masonic Flag Carrier would amuse you The following passages are exact quotes from The Southern Baptist Convention and Freemasonry by James Holly President of Mission and Ministry To Men N Beaumont TX The inside cover of the book states Mission Ministry to Men hereby grants permission for the reproduction of part or all of this booklet with two provisions one the material is not changed and two the source is I have followed these Freemasonry is one of the allies of the Devil Page The issue here is not moderate or conservative the issue is God and the Devil Page It is worthwhile to remember that the formulators of public school education in America were Freemasons Page Jesus Christ never commanded toleration as a motive for His disciples and toleration is the antithesis of the Christian Page The central dynamic of the Freemason drive for world unity through fraternity liberty and equality is This is seen in the writings of the 'great' writers of Freemasonry Page He Jesus Christ established the most sectarian of all possible Page For narrowness and sectarianism there is no equal to the Lord Jesus Christ Page What seems so right in the interest of toleration and its cousins liberty equality and fraternity is actually one of the subtlest lies of the 'father of ' Page The Southern Baptist Convention has many churches which were founded in the Lodge and which have corner stones dedicated by the Each of these churches should hold public ceremonies of repentance and of praying the blood and the Name of the Lord Jesus Christ over the church and renouncing the oaths taken at the dedication of the church and or Page I hope you all had a good laugh I know I did g Tony I appreciate the narrow mindedness of the view expressed in the text you I also appreciate your being amused by such determined Without taking anything away from your mirth I want to say that these views sadden I can only hope that that sort of narrow mindedness will die with the generations that have promoted Teach your children wet blanket mode off John John Luther Anybody who mistakes my Best for Email opinions for UMR's just doesn't know